Thanks to everyone for participating and your thoughtful questions and input. -Shak #ShakiraEdChat
In Col with our schools we’ve seen crime rates drop & gangs disband. Kids who'd have been recruited are on the way to univ. #ShakiraEdChat
Preschool costs ~ $8k per year per child. Juvenile detention costs ~ $90k per year per child. Again-numbers don’t lie. #ShakiraEdChat
RT @JasonPfeifle: Why is more 0-3 investment so critical for closing the income-based achievement gap? What's next step? @arneduncan @shakira #ShakiraEdChat
#ShakiraEdChat It’s key to have comprehensive programs, teacher training, AND work with the parents to work in challenging environments
RT @YoSoyFanShakira: #ShakiraEdChat How can education change a baby‘s life if its environment isn‘t  good?
.@isaura_cd De 0 a 3, todos los niños son genios lingüísticos por su plasticidad cerebral. A través de los idiomas enseñamos la globalidad
RT @isaura_cd: Te parece importante que los ninos aprendan varios idiomas ?  Por que y a partir de que edad deberian hacerlo ?  #ShakiraEdChat @shakira
.@Its_Pema poverty is perpetuated by the lack of opportunities like universal access to quality ed. Education is a birthright-not a luxury
.@keithdhardy spending time with their kids, sending them to school early, giving them nutrition, stimulation and love
RT @keithdhardy: What is the #1 thing families can do to promote their child's early education? #ShakiraEdChat @shakira @arneduncan
RT @Its_Pema: Can you really improve the situation without dealing with poverty, the root of this problem first? #ShakiraEdChat
.@Tayosaid Porqué he visto los milagros que logra en niños, familias, y comunidades enteras en Colombia y en otros países donde trabajamos
RT @Tayosaid: #ShakiraEdChat Para Ti Porque Es Inportante La Educacion?
.@ShakNewsQuilla Cualquier niño puede aprender idiomas antes de los 3-a Milan lo exponemos al esp, catalán, ing, francés, aleman, ruso,chino
RT @ShakNewsQuilla: @shakira ¿Se le puede enseñar a nuestros niños de primera infancia en dos idiomas? Por ejemplo, inglés y español #ShakiraEdChat
.@SHAKITINILOCA teaching them that education is an equalizer that gives us all the same chances no matter what conditions we’re born into
RT @SHAKITINILOCA: #ShakiraEdChat Shakira what are ways we can teach our children the importance of education so they can do their best in succeeding thank u
Agree! RT @arneduncan .@FeimM Please challenge all political leaders to invest in high quality learning opportunities for children 0-5.
.@saleosol education turns kids into productive citizens, is proven to boost GDPs of nations, and promotes global security and stability.
RT @saleosol: Why do you believe that education is the key to a better world?  #ShakiraEdChat @shakira
.@PreschoolNation Chile's model increased funds for ECD & schools , virtually eliminated illiteracy & drastically improved teacher training
RT @PreschoolNation: Can’t wait for the #ShakiraEdChat tomorrow! @Shakira @ArneDuncan what can the USA learn from international #earlyed models?
.@KnowledgeAll Fund. pies descalzos es parte de una alianza con el gob. Nal. "Primero lo primero". Abriremos 24 centros de DIT para 2016!
.@DJRarela showing leaders how early ed gives back & sharing success stories of transformed communities strengthens the case for investing
RT @DJRarela: .@shakira @arneduncan what, in your opinion, is the best way to motivate communities to invest in early education? #ShakiraEdChat
RT @arneduncan: .@LaurenEBarwick Zip code & family background should never determine ed quality. Education must be the great equalizer #ShakiraEdChat
.@Anna_Isabel05 kids are able 2 comprehend more than we think-It’s never too early 2 start teaching&exposing them to books even as newborns
RT @Anna_Isabel05: @shakira if you could change one thing in education system, what would it be? #ShakiraEdChat
RT @KnowledgeAll: @arneduncan @shaikra What does the investment in early ed look like in Colombia? #ShakiraEdChat
.@theonlywayisjam growing up surrounded by inequality made me intolerant to it, & research showed me that education was the solution to it

RT @theonlywayisjam: What influenced you into devoting so much of your life to education and early education?
#ShakiraEdChat @Shakira @ArneDuncan
RT @ShakiraQuilla: ¿Por qué todos debemos reconocer que la Educación Temprana es en la actualidad un tema de mucha importancia? #ShakiraEdChat @shakira
.@ShakiraQuilla hemos aprendido que se debe educar desde los inicios para poder solventar los desafíos que se encuentran mas adelante
.@Mellisebasan de acuerdo. faltan mas escuelas en los campos, mas compromisos de los gobiernos y el sector privado. Hay que presionar
RT @Mellisebasan: @Shakira #ShakiraEdChat por que no se hace una campaña para la construccion y remodelación de escuelas en zonas rurales? Así mejorar la educ
.@stumpteacher babies have an innate thirst for knowledge and enjoy learning-making it fun through focused play is another way of bonding.
RT @stumpteacher: .@arneduncan My biggest question/concern is how to keep joy and play in Early Ed in this era of testing/standards. @shakira #ShakiraEdChat
.@CO7649 Every $1 invested in early ed for disadvantaged kids has a return of at least 10% & reduces social spending. Numbers don’t lie!
RT @CO7649: #shakiraedchat is there a way to  distribute funds to the more needy schools. I believe the return on the dollar would be the highest there.
RT @JoseRendon0: @shakira Investing in education is the key to eradicating poverty, but where do you think our primary focus should be? #ShakiraEdChat
.@JoseRendon0 In ECD, bc kids who access it are better prepared to learn through primary, secondary & higher ed, and thrive throughout life
.@keithdhardy unequal access to ed. affects nations rich & poor, but in the US school dropouts will be reduced by increasing ECD programs
RT @keithdhardy: What r the major ECD differences in poor countries vs rich countries & how can we learn from each other? #ShakiraEdChat @shakira @arneduncan
.@cynthiapve se desarrollan aptitudes cognitivas, motrices, sociales y de conducta que resultan en ninos exitosos en la escuela y la vida
RT @cynthiapve: #ShakiraEdChat @shakira ¿Cuáles son las aptitudes que se adquieren con la educación temprana? Gracias.
.@GuilleShak now I know that i'm my child’s first educator-spending time teaching him is so key since his brain is rapidly developing.
RT @GuilleShak: How do you see the education now you're mum? #ShakiraEdChat @shakira
.@arneduncan Thank you for having me and taking the time to chat about an issue that’s close to both your heart & mine. Shak #ShakiraEdChat
